race.comment: ALPINE KANDY (4) blinkers go on for the first time and proven at this track and trip. Was fair on the line at her second run back when fifth over 1900m at Newcastle. Senior rider goes on from the inside gate. Sure to be thereabouts. THINK WE'RE THERE (3) fifth-up now and gripped on late at the good odds when a narrow second over 1900m at Newcastle. Looking for the extra ground and gets his chance. RHINESTONE LAD (7) racing in good style over this trip and maps to get the gun run after closing late when fourth over 2100m at Beaumont (Newcastle). Top-three player. DR EVIL (2) will find this a little easier after chipping away late when fifth over 1800m at Randwick in Highway grade. Keep safe with the claim.
